les 2, Clarke 2, Keenan, W Williams\n| con1 = Phil Castles 5\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = Petterson\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Victoria Park 2\n| attendance = 4500\n| referee = Thompson\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 3 May\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Ponsonby\n| score = 26-3\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Championship Games Commence/Ponsonby V Grafton\n| page =9\n| publisher = New Zealand Herald, Volume LVI, Issue 17152\n| date = 1919-04-05\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19190505.2.123.1\n| accessdate = 2019-08-19}}</ref>| away = Grafton\n| try1 = D Norgrove, S Chatfield, L Cadman, [[Bill Walsh (rugby league)|Bill Walsh]] 2, Cook\n| con1 = [[Thomas McClymont]] 4\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = Montgomery\n| con2 =\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Auckland Domain\n| attendance = 500\n| referee = [[William Wynyard (rugby league)|William Wynyard]]\n}}\n \n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 3 May\n| time = 3:00\n| home = Otahuhu\n| score = 3-28\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Championship Games Commence/North Shore V Otahuhu\n| page =9\n| publisher = New Zealand Herald, Volume LVI, Issue 17152\n| date = 1919-04-05\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19190505.2.123.1\n| accessdate = 2019-08-19}}</ref>\n| away = North Shore\n| try1 = Hyland\n| con1 =\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = Waters, [[Arthur Matthews (rugby league)|Arthur Matthews]], McAneny 3, Nelson\n| con2 = McAneny 3, Unknown 2 goals\n| pen2 =\n| stadium = Otahuhu\n| attendance =\n| referee =\n}}\n\n===Round 2===\n{{rugbybox collapsible\n| date = 10 May\n| time = 3:00\n| home = North Shore\n| score = 3-16\n| report = <ref>{{cite news\n| title =Championships Continue/City V North Shore\n| page =5\n| publisher = New Zealand Herald, Volume LVI, Issue 17158\n| date = 1919-05-12\n| url =https://paperspast.natlib.govt.nz/newspapers/NZH19190512.2.21.2\n| accessdate = 2019-08-19}}</ref>\n| away = City\n| try1 = L Boon\n| con1 =\n| pen1 =\n| try2 = H Wynn, [[Tom Haddon]], G Reed, Clarke\n| co